      <title>咖啡贸易商争相在欧盟森林砍伐法出台前运送咖啡豆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-02/coffee-traders-rush-to-ship-beans-ahead-of-eu-deforestation-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[咖啡货物大量涌入欧盟，因为贸易商们急于在年底生效的新环保法规之前囤积咖啡豆。彭博新闻社的 Ondiro Oganga 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就中东和非洲视野进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-02/coffee-traders-rush-to-ship-beans-ahead-of-eu-deforestation-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 07:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
