    <item>
      <title>Investcorp 联席首席执行官 Ben-Gacem 任职三十年后即将离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/investcorp-co-ceo-ben-gacem-set-to-leave-after-three-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为中东地区最大的另类资产管理公司之一，该公司将失去其任职 30 年的资深高管之一，这是该公司进行大规模改组的一部分，董事长穆罕默德·阿拉尔迪 (Mohammed Alardhi) 将接任首席执行官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/investcorp-co-ceo-ben-gacem-set-to-leave-after-three-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 05:55:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称黑石集团即将以 130 亿美元收购 AirTrunk</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/blackstone-is-said-to-near-a-20-billion-deal-to-acquire-airtrunk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，黑石公司即将达成协议，以超过 200 亿澳元（135 亿美元）的价格（包括债务）收购澳大利亚数据中心运营商 AirTrunk，这可能是今年最大的数字基础设施交易之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/blackstone-is-said-to-near-a-20-billion-deal-to-acquire-airtrunk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 05:25:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将在 2025 年创纪录地削减外汇稳定基金规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/south-korea-to-cut-fx-stabilization-fund-by-a-record-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国明年将把外汇稳定基金规模削减 30% 以上，创下历史新高，但政府表示，这仍然足以捍卫韩元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/south-korea-to-cut-fx-stabilization-fund-by-a-record-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 04:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 增产迹象和中国问题导致油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明 OPEC+ 将推进自 10 月起增产计划，而中国经济逆风加剧，油价因此下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:19:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：中国经济未显复苏迹象，股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/asia-eyes-cautious-open-after-china-factory-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国支持疲弱经济的努力没有取得任何成效，全球股市在连续四个月上涨之后，9 月份开始走下坡路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/asia-eyes-cautious-open-after-china-factory-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 22:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汉莎航空首席执行官前往葡萄牙参加政府关于 TAP 的会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/lufthansa-ceo-heads-to-portugal-for-government-talks-on-tap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国汉莎航空集团首席执行官卡斯滕·施波尔 (Carsten Spohr) 将于周一与葡萄牙政府官员会面，该德国航空集团正在考虑对国有航空公司葡萄牙航空公司 (TAP SA) 进行投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/lufthansa-ceo-heads-to-portugal-for-government-talks-on-tap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:55:28 GMT</pubDate>
